title: Man takes a sex quiz at the beach but viewers are distracted by this woman’s totally transparent top
text:
Mrs Crunch Sea View Man takes a sex quiz at the beach but viewers are distracted by this woman’s totally transparent top 
YouTube video has gone viral but not for the reasons the interviewer intended By Alison Maloney 3rd February 2017, 1:42 pm A VIDEO quiz about sex has gone viral – but not because of the near-the-knuckle answers. 
Instead, viewers have been obsessing about one girl’s very sheer vest top which left nothing to the imagination. YouTube / Adrian Gee Steph’s top got a lot of attention 
YouTuber Adrian Gee went to the beach to quiz women on what they like in bed. 
But pretty beachgoer Steph’s very visible boobs soon became the talking point when the video was uploaded. 
One viewer commented: “You can literally see both her breasts. 
Another said: “What’s the point of even wearing a top.” 
A third added: “Those nipples…. am blind now.” 
One joker wrote: “Fun fact: Not a single guy looked into that chick’s face.” 
The clip has been shared more than 670,000 times, with many admitting they only clicked on it because of Steph picture. Her chat didn’t disappoint either – especially her views on circumcision. 
Asked if she preferred a circumcised willy she told Adrian she didn’t because “It looks like an alien. It kind of stares at you.” 
Luckily no one was really listening. 
Yesterday, online Twitch players got an eyeful when a female gamer suffered a nip slip while adjusting her top. YouTube / Adrian Gee
